title: Morn Chernin
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Morn Chernin is a male human, recognizable for his distinctive jewelry (anklet). He has high Dexterity and low Constitution. He has a talent: he is an expert dart thrower and rock skipper. He tends to use flower speech or long words and is friendly in his dealings with others.

He is protective of close family members. If you asked him, he would say that his Ideal is, "Retribution!" If he has a flaw, it is that he has a forbidden love or is susceptible to romance.